trans-unit.source: The <unmanagedCodeEntityReference>Get File Properties</unmanagedCodeEntityReference> operation returns all user-defined metadata, standard HTTP properties, and system properties for the file.
trans-unit.target: The <unmanagedCodeEntityReference>Get File Properties</unmanagedCodeEntityReference> operation returns all user-defined metadata, standard HTTP properties, and system properties for the file.

trans-unit.source: It does not return the content of the file.
trans-unit.target: It does not return the content of the file.
